paragraphs.text:
%livy2.spark
import org.apache.spark.sql.types.DoubleType

val renameCare= deleteCare.withColumnRenamed("Facility Name","Facility_Name").withColumnRenamed("Ownership Type","Ownership_Type").withColumnRenamed("Certification Date","Certification_Date").withColumnRenamed("Total Number of Beds","Total_Number_of_Beds")

val convertCare = renameCare.withColumn(
    "Total_Number_of_Beds_Double",
    renameCare("Total_Number_of_Beds").cast(DoubleType)).drop("Total_Number_of_Beds").withColumnRenamed("Total_Number_of_Beds_Double", "Total_Number_of_Beds")

convertCare.count()
convertCare.printSchema()
convertCare.show(100)
